@startuml
title 16 - Fluxo Alternativo - Exceção na Entrega e Notificação

autonumber
participant "Carrier/Provider" as Provider
queue "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "Tracking Service" as Tracking
database "Tracking DB" as TrackingDb
participant "Order Service" as Order
participant "Notification Service" as Notification
actor Buyer as Comprador

Provider -> Kafka: CarrierTrackingEventIntegrationEvent status=Exception
Kafka -> Tracking: Consome evento do carrier
activate Tracking
Tracking -> TrackingDb: Verifica inbox e providerEventId
Tracking -> TrackingDb: Persiste TrackingEvent
Tracking -> TrackingDb: Atualiza ShipmentTracking para Exception
Tracking -> Kafka: TrackingStatusChangedIntegrationEvent currentStatus=Exception
deactivate Tracking

Kafka -> Order: TrackingStatusChangedIntegrationEvent
activate Order
Order -> Order: Avalia impacto no pedido
alt Exceção recuperável
  Order -> Order: Mantém pedido ativo
else Exceção terminal
  Order -> Order: Marca pedido em análise operacional
end
deactivate Order

Kafka -> Notification: TrackingStatusChangedIntegrationEvent currentStatus=Exception
activate Notification
Notification -> Notification: Mapeia para DeliveryException
Notification -> Notification: Aplica preferência do comprador
Notification --> Comprador: Notifica problema na entrega e próxima ação
deactivate Notification

@enduml
